Data Analysis with SQL and Data Storytelling
BOOTCAMP PROJECT CHALLENGE RESULTS: BRADESCO: GENAI and DATA (Accelerate Your Learning with AI: Explore the Power of NotebookLM)

This repository documents an authorial study conducted with the support of NotebookLM, in which I actively participated in source curation (including technical books), defining the study methodology, and requesting educational artifacts such as flashcards, slides, and mind maps to consolidate learning.

The focus of the study is to understand how Data Analysis with SQL, combined with Data Storytelling, directly impacts the way analytical results are understood and used in decision-making.

