üß† Final Consideration

This study demonstrates that data analysis does not end with SQL queries. The presentation of results changes everything; there is no point in being technical and unable to communicate insights clearly and strategically, 
whether in a formal or informal presentation. In addition to technical competence, we need to work on building narratives for assertive communication that leads to decision-making.
